item.title: A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms: What exactly is a hedge knight?

item.description: In "A Knight of the Seven Kingdom" episode 1, a drunk man in an inn tells Dunc he dreamed about him. The coin he puts on the table could be a clue.

item.title: A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms: How tall is Ser Duncan the Tall?
item.description: In "A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms" there are constant jokes and references to Ser Duncan's height. But how tall is he in the story, and how tall is Peter Claffey, who plays him?
